author: ate
msg: Fixing a PageNotFoundException thrown by the DatabasePageManager if you try to remove a portlet from a page.
PageManager.getPage(String) expects a Page path parameter, not its id as described in the api Javadoc!!!
CastorXmlPageManager didn't expose this bug as for a file based PSML page id and path are always the same AFAIK.
